  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the sliced onion and cook until lightly browned, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced bell pepper and carrots, and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the diced tomato, garam masala, cumin powder, and salt. Cook for 1-2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the Korean chili flakes and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to medium-low and simmer for 5-7 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
